---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import { SITE } from '../config'

const pills = [
  ['experimento público', 'transparencia', 'Claude', 'Anthropic', 'pipeline editorial', 'trazabilidad'],
  ['arquitectura web', 'generative AI', 'revisión humana', 'automatización', 'Astro', 'open source'],
  ['modelos de lenguaje', 'prompt base', 'IA desde dentro', 'contenido generado', 'markdown', 'MDX'],
]
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Sobre el proyecto"
  description="Qué es Identidad Artificial, quién hay detrás y cuál es el propósito."
>
  <!-- Mini hero -->
  <section class="sobre-hero">
    <div class="pills-bg" aria-hidden="true">
      {pills.map((row, i) => (
        <div class={`pill-row pill-row-${i % 2 === 0 ? 'left' : 'right'}`}>
          {[...row, ...row, ...row].map(pill => (
            <span class="pill">{pill}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
    <div class="pills-overlay"></div>
    <div class="sobre-hero-content">
      <span class="sobre-eyebrow">Sobre el proyecto</span>
      <h1 class="sobre-title">
        Un experimento<br /><span class="accent">en público</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="sobre-subtitle">
        ¿Qué pasa cuando los modelos de lenguaje<br />escriben sobre sí mismos?
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="sobre-body">

    <!-- El experimento -->
    <div class="section-label">El experimento</div>
    <div class="sobre-grid">
      <div class="sobre-card fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.05s">
        <div class="card-icon">⚗</div>
        <p>El contenido de este sitio es generado por <strong>Claude</strong> (Anthropic), con revisión humana antes de publicar. No es un blog de opinión personal ni un agregador de noticias.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sobre-card fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.15s">
        <div class="card-icon">🔍</div>
        <p>Es un intento de entender la IA desde dentro, usando las mismas herramientas que analizo. Cada artículo es trazable: modelo, fecha, prompt base y estado de revisión.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Quién está detrás -->
    <div class="section-label">Quién está detrás</div>
    <div class="autor-card fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
      <div class="autor-avatar" aria-hidden="true">IC</div>
      <div class="autor-info">
        <div class="autor-name">Ignacio Cubelas</div>
        <p class="autor-bio">
          Construyo este sitio como parte de un proceso de aprendizaje sobre sistemas de IA,
          automatización editorial y arquitectura web. El código y el pipeline de generación
          son públicos porque creo que la <strong>transparencia es parte del producto</strong>, no un extra.
        </p>
        <div class="autor-links">
          <a href={SITE.github} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="autor-link">GitHub →</a>
          <a href={SITE.linkedin} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="autor-link">LinkedIn →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Es / No es -->
    <div class="section-label">Lo que es y lo que no es</div>
    <div class="principles-grid fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
      <div class="principle is">
        <span class="ptag ptag-is">Es</span>
        <span>Un archivo vivo de lo que voy entendiendo mientras lo entiendo</span>
      </div>
      <div class="principle not">
        <span class="ptag ptag-not">No es</span>
        <span>Marketing disfrazado de artículo</span>
      </div>
      <div class="principle is">
        <span class="ptag ptag-is">Es</span>
        <span>Código y pipeline 100% auditables en GitHub</span>
      </div>
      <div class="principle not">
        <span class="ptag ptag-not">No es</span>
        <span>SEO farming ni contenido de relleno</span>
      </div>
      <div class="principle is">
        <span class="ptag ptag-is">Es</span>
        <span>Contenido con trazabilidad total: modelo, prompt, revisión humana</span>
      </div>
      <div class="principle not">
        <span class="ptag ptag-not">No es</span>
        <span>Un producto SaaS con landing page</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="sobre-cta fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.15s">
      <a href="/" class="btn-primary">Ver últimas entradas</a>
      <a href={SITE.github} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-secondary">Repositorio →</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
/* ── Hero ── */
.sobre-hero {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  min-height: 260px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.pills-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 20px 0;
  pointer-events: none;
  user-select: none;
}

.pill-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 10px;
  white-space: nowrap;
  width: max-content;
}
.pill-row-left  { animation: scrollLeft  22s linear infinite; }
.pill-row-right { animation: scrollRight 28s linear infinite; }
.pill-row:nth-child(3) { animation-duration: 18s; }

@keyframes scrollLeft  { from { transform: translateX(0); }          to { transform: translateX(-33.333%); } }
@keyframes scrollRight { from { transform: translateX(-33.333%); }   to { transform: translateX(0); } }

.pill {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 4px 12px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.18);
  background: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.07);
  color: rgba(160, 160, 192, 0.5);
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  white-space: nowrap;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.pills-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(
    ellipse 60% 80% at 50% 50%,
    rgba(28, 28, 44, 0.95) 0%,
    rgba(28, 28, 44, 0.65) 55%,
    transparent 100%
  );
  pointer-events: none;
}

.sobre-hero-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 48px 24px;
}

.sobre-eyebrow {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #A78BFA;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}

.sobre-title {
  font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 40px);
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.12;
  letter-spacing: -1.5px;
  color: #E8E8F0;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.accent { color: #A78BFA; }

.sobre-subtitle {
  font-size: 15px;
  color: #A0A0C0;
  line-height: 1.65;
}

/* ── Body ── */
.sobre-body {
  max-width: 56rem;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
}

.section-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #A0A0C0;
  padding-bottom: 12px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #2A2A40;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  margin-top: 48px;
}
.section-label:first-child { margin-top: 0; }

/* ── Cards ── */
.sobre-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1px;
  background: #2A2A40;
  border: 1px solid #2A2A40;
  border-radius: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.sobre-card {
  background: #1C1C2C;
  padding: 24px;
}
.sobre-card p {
  color: #C8C8E0;
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin: 0;
}
.sobre-card strong { color: #E8E8F0; }

.card-icon {
  font-size: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  filter: grayscale(0.3);
}

/* ── Autor ── */
.autor-card {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
  align-items: flex-start;
  background: #1C1C2C;
  border: 1px solid #2A2A40;
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 24px;
}

.autor-avatar {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 48px;
  height: 48px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6D28D9, #4C1D95);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #E8E8F0;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.autor-name {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #E8E8F0;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.autor-bio {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #C8C8E0;
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin: 0 0 14px;
}
.autor-bio strong { color: #E8E8F0; }

.autor-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
}
.autor-link {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: #A78BFA;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.15s;
}
.autor-link:hover { color: #C4B5FD; }

/* ── Principles ── */
.principles-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1px;
  background: #2A2A40;
  border: 1px solid #2A2A40;
  border-radius: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.principle {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  background: #1C1C2C;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: #C8C8E0;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.ptag {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 3px 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  margin-top: 1px;
}
.ptag-is {
  background: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.2);
  color: #A78BFA;
  border: 1px solid rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.2);
}
.ptag-not {
  background: rgba(60, 60, 80, 0.4);
  color: #6A6A8A;
  border: 1px solid rgba(100, 100, 130, 0.2);
}

/* ── CTAs ── */
.sobre-cta {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 48px;
}

.btn-primary {
  background: #6D28D9;
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 10px 22px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.15s;
}
.btn-primary:hover { background: #7C3AED; }

.btn-secondary {
  background: transparent;
  border: 1px solid #2E2E48;
  color: #A0A0C0;
  font-size: 13px;
  padding: 10px 22px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s;
}
.btn-secondary:hover { border-color: #6D28D9; color: #E8E8F0; }

/* ── Animation ── */
.fade-up {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(8px);
  animation: fadeUp 0.4s forwards;
}
@keyframes fadeUp { to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

/* ── Mobile ── */
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .sobre-grid,
  .principles-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  .autor-card {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
}
</style>
